:: \ ch1_004 {"position":"700,800","size":"100,100"}
The man doesn't say anything, he merely starts bending down towards his shoe, starts looking for something. His quiet moans echo across the pits of your stomach. Sickening.

He brings one hand up.

Old Man: "Here it is." In his dirty open palm, he shows you a single gold coin.

[["I suppose you get to stay in the boat for now." |You get to stay]]


:: "I doubt you'll find her in here. This place is for the dead, old man." {"position":"700,1300","size":"100,100"}
Old Man:

He snivels once over and I notice a tear dropping from his eye. I have never been versed in this. Should I even care?

"Penelope... Penelope... I'm sorry, I'm so sorry." He breaks down onto the table.

[[Start leaving.]]
[["Please try to recollect yourself."]]


:: "I'm not Penelope." {"position":"700,1675","size":"100,100"}
Old Man: "You're not..." He shrieks quietly. "Of course you're not. The voices. They are so loud. They are so numerous. They are... I can almost hear her voice. Her sweet voice."

[["Who are you talking about?" |"What does she look like?"]]


:: "I'm not your errand boy." {"position":"700,1875","size":"100,100"}
Old Man:

"I didn't mean it in that way." Tries to recompose himself. Wipes a tear. Turns his head to face me straight up. My stomach yirks. "I do apologize. I will not bother you anymore. But I beg of you. She's a baby. If you see her, let me know..."

[[I stay in silence. |continue001]]


:: "Is your daughter dead, too?" {"position":"675,2125","size":"100,100"}
Old Man:

Another tear trickles down his face. "Yes. She passed when she was only two months old." His mouth quakes as he leans down onto his hands once more. "She has to be here somewhere."

[["She's in a better place than here, I assure you."]]
[["The chances of finding such a small baby in this boat are slim to none."]]


:: "It should hurt, you piece of shit." {"position":"700,1550","size":"100,100"}
Old Man: "I suppose I deserve that. I know. I know you deserved more... Penelope."

[["I'm not Penelope."]]
[["What your mouth."]]


